really powerful teachings,

00:28:31.650 --> 00:28:34.470 align:middle line:84%
and he's a very good
vehicle for the message.

00:28:34.470 --> 00:28:37.860 align:middle line:84%
>> He knew the
power of initiative.

00:28:37.860 --> 00:28:41.370 align:middle line:84%
He didn't wait for anybody
