00:28:47.620 --> 00:28:51.200 align:middle line:10%
It was like sending
out an e-blast today.

00:28:51.200 --> 00:28:54.690 align:middle line:84%
>> What Yogananda did that was
profound for Americans was talk

00:28:54.690 --> 00:28:56.880 align:middle line:84%
