personal relationship with

00:28:56.880 --> 00:28:57.680 align:middle line:90%
the Divine.

00:28:57.680 --> 00:29:01.300 align:middle line:90%


00:29:01.300 --> 00:29:05.700 align:middle line:10%
>> I was a totally
frustrated man.

00:29:05.700 --> 00:29:09.990 align:middle line:10%
I had thought money
could give me happiness,

00:29:09.990 --> 00:29:11.970 align:middle line:10%
but nothing seemed
to satisfy me.

00:29:11.970 --> 00:29:14.890 align:middle line:90%


00:29:14.890 --> 00:29:17.260 align:middle line:84%
I was skeptical,
like everyone was.

00:29:17.260 --> 00:29:21.060 align:middle line:90%


00:29:21.060 --> 00:29:23.750 align:middle line:10%
>> Sit straight,
shoulder blades together,

00:29:23.750 --> 00:29:25.960 align:middle line:10%
chin parallel to the ground.

00:29:25.960 --> 00:29:29.140 align:middle line:10%
Concentrate on the point
between the eyebrows--

00:29:29.140 --> 00:29:34.600 align:middle line:10%
center of thought and
will and concentration.

00:29:34.600 --> 00:29:37.270 align:middle line:10%
And again and again,
say, "Reveal Thyself"

00:29:37.270 --> 00:29:43.024 align:middle line:10%
as joy and wisdom and
spiritual perception.

00:29:43.024 --> 00:29:46.482 align:middle line:10%
Again and again say,
"Reveal Thyself."

00:29:46.482 --> 00:29:51.930 align:middle line:90%


00:29:51.930 --> 00:29:55.080 align:middle line:84%
>> James Lynn was a
wealthy industrialist,

00:29:55.080 --> 00:29:59.490 align:middle line:84%
and he went on to become a very
close devotee and an important

00:29:59.490 --> 00:30:04.860 align:middle line:84%
benefactor of Yogananda's
work around the country.

00:30:04.860 --> 00:30:07.740 align:middle line:84%
>> Many who joined his classes
stepped forward and wrote

00:30:07.740 --> 00:30:11.160 align:middle line:84%
checks, trying to
keep Yogananda in L.A.

00:30:11.160 --> 00:30:13.440 align:middle line:90%
>> And he saw such enthusiasm.

00:30:13.440 --> 00:30:19.350 align:middle line:10%
He thought, this is the
place to establish a center.

00:30:19.350 --> 00:30:22.140 align:middle line:84%
>> When I saw the large
building on the crest of Mount

00:30:22.140 --> 00:30:26.120 align:middle line:84%
Washington, I
recognized it at once.

00:30:26.120 --> 00:30:29.477 align:middle line:90%
>> As he saw, this is the place.

00:30:29.477 --> 00:30:31.310 align:middle line:84%
>> This became the
headquarters of his work.

00:30:31.310 --> 00:30:34.030 align:middle line:90%


00:30:34.030 --> 00:30:36.850 align:middle line:84%
Yogananda called it the
"spiritual White House,"

00:30:36.850 --> 00:30:39.430 align:middle line:84%
and it was a place
where he gave classes.

00:30:39.430 --> 00:30:42.790 align:middle line:10%
He even had rooms available to
rent with the idea of starting

00:30:42.790 --> 00:30:44.920 align:middle line:10%
a spiritual community.

00:30:44.920 --> 00:30:46.840 align:middle line:84%
And the first event
he held there,

00:30:46.840 --> 00:30:49.090 align:middle line:84%
before the property
was even purchased,

00:30:49.090 --> 00:30:51.240 align:middle line:90%
was an Easter Sunrise service.

00:30:51.240 --> 00:30:56.060 align:middle line:10%
>> True Christianity has
been lost and forgotten.

00:30:56.060 --> 00:30:58.780 align:middle line:10%
And what the Ancients
taught in India

00:30:58.780 --> 00:31:01.540 align:middle line:10%
has been lost and forgotten.

00:31:01.540 --> 00:31:07.060 align:middle line:10%
Those ought to be revived as
one highway to the infinite.

00:31:07.060 --> 00:31:10.090 align:middle line:84%
>> One of the keys to
Yogananda's popularity

00:31:10.090 --> 00:31:14.740 align:middle line:84%
in America was his love
and affection for Jesus.

00:31:14.740 --> 00:31:18.960 align:middle line:84%
He placed Jesus on the
altar with his lineage

00:31:18.960 --> 00:31:21.030 align:middle line:90%
and with Krishna.

00:31:21.030 --> 00:31:24.620 align:middle line:84%
>> He said that Jesus really was
representing to us this is who

00:31:24.620 --> 00:31:25.420 align:middle line:90%
you are.

00:31:25.420 --> 00:31:27.900 align:middle line:10%
This is your ability
to open yourself

00:31:27.900 --> 00:31:29.790 align:middle line:10%
to the Divine Mystery
in ways that you never

00:31:29.790 --> 00:31:31.530 align:middle line:10%
thought were possible.

00:31:31.530 --> 00:31:33.820 align:middle line:90%
>> Jesus is revered in India.

00:31:33.820 --> 00:31:36.000 align:middle line:90%
People don't realize that.

00:31:36.000 --> 00:31:41.130 align:middle line:84%
But he is held to be either
an incarnation of God

00:31:41.130 --> 00:31:45.220 align:middle line:84%
or, at the very
least, a supreme yogi.

00:31:45.220 --> 00:31:48.190 align:middle line:10%
>> The value of Yogananda's
teaching was that he picked up

00:31:48.190 --> 00:31:52.390 align:middle line:10%
on this angle, that there is
this universal opportunity

00:31:52.390 --> 00:31:55.660 align:middle line:10%
to understand who we are.

00:31:55.660 --> 00:31:58.130 align:middle line:84%
What is true of Jesus is
also true of all of us.

00:31:58.130 --> 00:32:00.670 align:middle line:90%


00:32:00.670 --> 00:32:02.530 align:middle line:84%
>> It's not about
religion at all.

00:32:02.530 --> 00:32:04.490 align:middle line:84%
It's about what's
behind religion--

00:32:04.490 --> 00:32:06.390 align:middle line:90%
meditation.

00:32:06.390 --> 00:32:07.417 align:middle line:90%
Meditate.

00:32:07.417 --> 00:32:08.250 align:middle line:90%
That's what he said.

00:32:08.250 --> 00:32:10.088 align:middle line:90%
Meditation is the catchword.

00:32:10.088 --> 00:32:14.390 align:middle line:90%


00:32:14.390 --> 00:32:17.890 align:middle line:84%
>> Yoga really is a
philosophical system.

00:32:17.890 --> 00:32:20.180 align:middle line:84%
A lot of people go
to yoga to look hot.

00:32:20.180 --> 00:32:22.220 align:middle line:84%
