give you flat abs,

00:32:22.220 --> 00:32:23.720 align:middle line:84%
even though that's
a nice byproduct.

00:32:23.720 --> 00:32:25.758 align:middle line:84%
It's really set up
to understand God.

00:32:25.758 --> 00:32:30.870 align:middle line:90%


00:32:30.870 --> 00:32:35.020 align:middle line:84%
>> Kriya Yoga is the science
of God-Realization through

00:32:35.020 --> 00:32:37.160 align:middle line:90%
meditation.

00:32:37.160 --> 00:32:41.980 align:middle line:84%
>> Yogananda did teach Hatha
Yoga as one way to prepare

00:32:41.980 --> 00:32:44.740 align:middle line:90%
for meditation.

00:32:44.740 --> 00:32:48.550 align:middle line:84%
>> He also developed this system
of energization exercises.

00:32:48.550 --> 00:32:52.120 align:middle line:90%


00:32:52.120 --> 00:32:54.020 align:middle line:10%
>> The tension exercises--

00:32:54.020 --> 00:32:57.370 align:middle line:10%
charge the body with the life
current from the universe.

00:32:57.370 --> 00:33:00.580 align:middle line:10%
Energy distributed
evenly in the body

00:33:00.580 --> 00:33:04.260 align:middle line:10%
is what the diseases
from settling.

00:33:04.260 --> 00:33:06.320 align:middle line:10%
You don't have to
be afraid of germs.

00:33:06.320 --> 00:33:11.810 align:middle line:10%
If your body is electrified,
they will be electrocuted.

00:33:11.810 --> 00:33:15.400 align:middle line:84%
>> Everything you do
affects your brain.

00:33:15.400 --> 00:33:18.320 align:middle line:84%
By tensing the muscles, you're
activating your frontal lobes.

00:33:18.320 --> 00:33:20.510 align:middle line:10%
If you lower the stress
hormones in the brain,

00:33:20.510 --> 00:33:22.660 align:middle line:10%
it lowers your blood
pressure and your heart rate,

00:33:22.660 --> 00:33:24.820 align:middle line:10%
and it gets your mind
prepared for doing whatever

00:33:24.820 --> 00:33:28.000 align:middle line:10%
it is that you're about to do.

00:33:28.000 --> 00:33:32.980 align:middle line:84%
>> Kriya Yoga teaches in the
spine are these instruments

00:33:32.980 --> 00:33:36.020 align:middle line:84%
of higher perception that
are normally dormant in most

00:33:36.020 --> 00:33:36.820 align:middle line:90%
people.

00:33:36.820 --> 00:33:40.960 align:middle line:90%


00:33:40.960 --> 00:33:44.020 align:middle line:84%
Through withdrawing that
energy and directing it

00:33:44.020 --> 00:33:46.900 align:middle line:84%
by concentration into
the spine and brain,

00:33:46.900 --> 00:33:51.120 align:middle line:84%
Yogananda said those instruments
of divine perceptions awaken.

00:33:51.120 --> 00:34:01.170 align:middle line:90%


00:34:01.170 --> 00:34:03.630 align:middle line:84%
The physical world is
not the highest reality.

00:34:03.630 --> 00:34:06.280 align:middle line:90%


00:34:06.280 --> 00:34:07.860 align:middle line:84%
>> When we have
a dream at night,

00:34:07.860 --> 00:34:12.210 align:middle line:84%
it feels incredibly real
while we're in the dream.

00:34:12.210 --> 00:34:14.880 align:middle line:84%
And then we wake up, and
we look at the reality

00:34:14.880 --> 00:34:17.730 align:middle line:84%
that we're now in, and we say,
oh OK, that was just a dream.

00:34:17.730 --> 00:34:22.130 align:middle line:90%


00:34:22.130 --> 00:34:24.770 align:middle line:84%
Well, when people have
mystical experiences they say,

00:34:24.770 --> 00:34:26.409 align:middle line:84%
well, this is the
ultimate reality.

00:34:26.409 --> 00:34:27.639 align:middle line:90%
This feels more real.

00:34:27.639 --> 00:34:30.530 align:middle line:90%


00:34:30.530 --> 00:34:33.144 align:middle line:84%
And all this other stuff, that's
not really the real reality.

00:34:33.144 --> 00:34:43.508 align:middle line:90%


00:34:43.508 --> 00:34:47.960 align:middle line:10%
>> Feel the life currents
ascending and descending

00:34:47.960 --> 00:34:50.900 align:middle line:10%
in the spine.

00:34:50.900 --> 00:34:53.449 align:middle line:10%
By mastery of the
intelligent life currents

00:34:53.449 --> 00:34:57.210 align:middle line:10%
in the central nervous
system, the body and brain

00:34:57.210 --> 00:34:58.010 align:middle line:10%
can be purified.

00:34:58.010 --> 00:35:00.880 align:middle line:90%


00:35:00.880 --> 00:35:05.180 align:middle line:84%
Go up and down the spine,
feeling the centers,

00:35:05.180 --> 00:35:08.000 align:middle line:90%
and mentally chanting "ohm."

00:35:08.000 --> 00:35:09.200 align:middle line:90%
[TYPEWRITER KEYS CLACKING]

00:35:09.200 --> 00:35:13.220 align:middle line:84%
>> Dear Guruji, I
have absorbed so much.

00:35:13.220 --> 00:35:18.380 align:middle line:10%
I will try to keep it all
within me and profit by it.

00:35:18.380 --> 00:35:21.330 align:middle line:84%
Self-Realization has
helped my career.

00:35:21.330 --> 00:35:24.290 align:middle line:10%
It has helped me to
think very little of me

00:35:24.290 --> 00:35:28.194 align:middle line:10%
and let the Great
Spirit pass through me.

