00:36:14.180 --> 00:36:17.120 align:middle line:90%
He was very well liked.

00:36:17.120 --> 00:36:20.550 align:middle line:84%
>> I'm powerless to tell
how greatly he has helped me

00:36:20.550 --> 00:36:25.790 align:middle line:84%
in carrying on my educational
work in India and Boston.

00:36:25.790 --> 00:36:29.270 align:middle line:84%
He successfully carried on
the work at the Ranchi school

00:36:29.270 --> 00:36:32.420 align:middle line:90%
during my absence from India.

00:36:32.420 --> 00:36:34.570 align:middle line:84%
>> This was his childhood
friend from Calcutta.

00:36:34.570 --> 00:36:37.170 align:middle line:90%


00:36:37.170 --> 00:36:39.360 align:middle line:84%
And I think as boys
both of them felt

00:36:39.360 --> 00:36:41.130 align:middle line:84%
