up to him after the meals.

00:37:00.575 --> 00:37:03.956 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC - "SUNDAY"]

00:37:03.956 --> 00:37:07.830 align:middle line:90%


00:37:07.830 --> 00:37:10.890 align:middle line:84%
>> The 1920s was a period
of almost ceaseless travel

00:37:10.890 --> 00:37:12.280 align:middle line:90%
