00:37:26.870 --> 00:37:29.050 align:middle line:90%
There is no path.

00:37:29.050 --> 00:37:31.300 align:middle line:84%
>> There were other
gurus who came.

00:37:31.300 --> 00:37:36.070 align:middle line:10%
Swami Vivekananda, whom
