00:37:54.695 --> 00:37:56.950 align:middle line:10%
>> In America everybody is busy.

00:37:56.950 --> 00:37:59.200 align:middle line:10%
And if you keep on running
after too many hobbies,

00:37:59.200 --> 00:38:01.720 align:middle line:10%
you won't have any
time left for bliss.

00:38:01.720 --> 00:38:13.480 align:middle line:90%


00:38:13.480 --> 00:38:15.520 align:middle line:10%
>> Everything was
covered in the lessons,

00:38:15.520 --> 00:38:17.920 align:middle line:10%
from how to achieve
success in our life,

00:38:17.920 --> 00:38:21.880 align:middle line:10%
magnetizing or attracting your
soul mate, creating abundance,

00:38:21.880 --> 00:38:28.030 align:middle line:10%
how to create harmony with
others, how to find happiness.

00:38:28.030 --> 00:38:32.130 align:middle line:84%
>> You people do
not sleep correctly.

00:38:32.130 --> 00:38:36.400 align:middle line:84%
You subconsciously
worry about unpaid bills

00:38:36.400 --> 00:38:40.410 align:middle line:84%
and allow your sleep
to be disturbed

00:38:40.410 --> 00:38:43.910 align:middle line:90%
by the mental movies of dreams.

00:38:43.910 --> 00:38:48.040 align:middle line:84%
By closing the eyes
and enough relaxation,

00:38:48.040 --> 00:38:52.640 align:middle line:84%
I can remain asleep
several nights.

00:38:52.640 --> 00:38:56.890 align:middle line:84%
And by opening the eyes
and recharging the body,

00:38:56.890 --> 00:38:58.750 align:middle line:90%
I can keep awake several days.

00:38:58.750 --> 00:39:02.130 align:middle line:90%


00:39:02.130 --> 00:39:05.070 align:middle line:84%
>> Willpower is really one
of the absolute necessities

00:39:05.070 --> 00:39:07.230 align:middle line:90%
for spiritual progress.

