00:39:13.360 --> 00:39:18.740 align:middle line:90%


00:39:18.740 --> 00:39:21.210 align:middle line:10%
>> He asked the six men to line
up with their hands on each

00:39:21.210 --> 00:39:25.440 align:middle line:10%
other's back, making a
line across the platform.

00:39:25.440 --> 00:39:29.820 align:middle line:84%
