01:10:44.365 --> 01:10:47.320 align:middle line:10%
is to explore it both
from sort of the outside

01:10:47.320 --> 01:10:48.490 align:middle line:10%
in and from the inside out.

01:10:48.490 --> 01:10:53.700 align:middle line:90%


01:10:53.700 --> 01:10:56.460 align:middle line:84%
>> Delusion is the belief that
there is something outside

01:10:56.460 --> 01:10:57.780 align:middle line:90%
of you.

01:10:57.780 --> 01:11:03.200 align:middle line:84%
But your happiness is not based
on anything outside of you--

01:11:03.200 --> 01:11:05.610 align:middle line:84%
