01:11:08.850 --> 01:11:10.500 align:middle line:90%
laughing.

01:11:10.500 --> 01:11:12.600 align:middle line:84%
So look inside for
the watcher and be

01:11:12.600 --> 01:11:17.470 align:middle line:84%
connected to the watcher,
and then be awake.

01:11:17.470 --> 01:11:21.240 align:middle line:90%


01:11:21.240 --> 01:11:25.530 align:middle line:10%
>> The Indian teachings that
Yogananda represented were not

01:11:25.530 --> 01:11:26.880 align:middle line:10%
escapes.

01:11:26.880 --> 01:11:32.070 align:middle line:10%
They were methods of
adapting to these upheavals

01:11:32.070 --> 01:11:35.040 align:middle line:10%
and these changes,
