01:11:35.040 --> 01:11:40.320 align:middle line:10%
that we are more than the
personality and the roles

01:11:40.320 --> 01:11:42.900 align:middle line:10%
that we play and
the body we inhabit.

01:11:42.900 --> 01:11:46.990 align:middle line:90%


01:11:46.990 --> 01:11:53.100 align:middle line:10%
>> When I am the soul, I know
