01:11:56.260 --> 01:11:58.550 align:middle line:10%
Only love is important.

01:11:58.550 --> 01:12:01.790 align:middle line:90%


01:12:01.790 --> 01:12:04.560 align:middle line:84%
>> If we're going to change
those kind of circumstances

01:12:04.560 --> 01:12:06.920 align:middle line:84%
so there's hope
for our survival,

01:12:06.920 --> 01:12:09.461 align:middle line:84%
the change has to
come from inside out.

01:12:09.461 --> 01:12:12.450 align:middle line:90%


01:12:12.450 --> 01:12:16.814 align:middle line:10%
>> A man who has reformed
himself will reform thousands.

01:12:16.814 --> 01:12:25.180 align:middle line:90%


01:12:25.180 --> 01:12:29.110 align:middle line:84%
>> Yogananda saw that if
there wasn't some way to reach

01:12:29.110 --> 01:12:31.720 align:middle line:84%
the masses with this
message of yoga--

01:12:31.720 --> 01:12:34.750 align:middle line:84%
