transition into the Atomic Age.

01:12:39.960 --> 01:12:42.010 align:middle line:10%
>> They were leading this
foundation at that time

01:12:42.010 --> 01:12:46.180 align:middle line:10%
to bring the teachings current,
so they can really create

01:12:46.180 --> 01:12:48.950 align:middle line:10%
a transformation on a
collective level in the world,

01:12:48.950 --> 01:12:50.590 align:middle line:10%
not just in the forest.

01:12:50.590 --> 01:12:51.700 align:middle line:90%
The forest is here now.

01:12:51.700 --> 01:12:54.572 align:middle line:84%
This is bigger and
