01:12:54.572 --> 01:12:56.280 align:middle line:84%
If you don't practice
the teachings here,

01:12:56.280 --> 01:12:57.779 align:middle line:84%
there will be no
forest left at all.

01:12:57.779 --> 01:13:08.368 align:middle line:90%


01:13:08.368 --> 01:13:10.980 align:middle line:84%
>> "The Autobiography"
was a doorway in.

01:13:10.980 --> 01:13:13.980 align:middle line:84%
It was a table-setter
