01:14:23.420 --> 01:14:24.220 align:middle line:90%
as a soul?

01:14:24.220 --> 01:14:26.970 align:middle line:90%


01:14:26.970 --> 01:14:30.390 align:middle line:10%
>> We have a far too limited
